the Pomona police station before beginning their shift. ; Photo, During his 
patrol, Tuttle checks for locked doors at a mall in Pomona. ; Photo, Sgt. Joe 
Romero is the unit's training officer; Darwin Tuttle drives past graffiti, and 
David Swift and a motorcycle officer call a tow truck. LOU MACK / Los Angeles 
Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
