young patient in a Punta Prieta, Mexico, clinic as a fellow volunteer doctor 
interprets.; Photo, COLOR, Above, people from nearby villages join those from 
Punta Prieta outside the clinic, located on the right.; Photo, COLOR, "Sams" 
board a cattle truck for the ride to the clinic, right, after landing at a 
local airstrip.; Photo, COLOR, Below, patients wait to be seen. ; Photo, An 
array of vitamins are stocked at the Bahia de Los Angeles. Dr. Dale Hoyt says 
vitamin deficiency is common among his patients. LAWRENCE K. HO / Los Angeles 
