MOLESTATION -- LOS ANGELES COUNTY; INTERVIEWING; MCFARLANE, KEE; CHILDREN'S 
INSTITUTE INTERNATIONAL; MISTAKES; THERAPY; MENTAL HEALTH; EMOTIONS; BEHAVIOR; 
PSYCHOLOGY; CHILD ABUSE; INVESTIGATIONS 
</P>
