<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
LOS ANGELES CLIPPERS (BASKETBALL TEAM); BASKETBALL TEAMS; BASKETBALL PLAYERS; 
SPORTS INJURIES; CASEY, DON; HARPER, RON; COACHES 
</P>
