<HEADLINE>
<P>
FULLERTON'S LUCZAJ NAMED BUENA PARK FOOTBALL COACH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By TOM HAMILTON, TIMES STAFF WRITER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Former Fullerton High School football coach Martin Luczaj, who turned a 
struggling program into a playoff participant for six consecutive seasons, has 
been named football coach at Buena Park. 
</P>
<P>
Luczaj, 36, compiled a 52-19 record, winning three league titles and leading 
Fullerton into the Central Conference championship game twice (one title) 
before he resigned in March 1987. 
</P>
<P>
Luczaj became Orange County's youngest head coach at 28 in 1981. Fullerton, 1-9 
in 1980, won the Freeway League title in Luczaj's first season with an 8-3 
record. 
</P>
<P>
Luczaj spent the past two years as Fullerton's baseball coach and as an 
assistant football coach at Fullerton College. 
</P>
<P>
Buena Park has struggled in the Freeway League during the past six years, 
losing 28 consecutive league games before defeating Sonora, 21-13, last fall. 
</P>
<P>
"Marty wanted to get back to coaching on the high school level and there are 
some distinct advantages at Buena Park," said Greg Bice, assistant 
superintendent in charge of personnel for the Fullerton Union High School 
District. 
</P>
<P>
"Buena Park has a very successful bingo program (generating funds for 
extracurricular activities) and the school has added a weight room and a 
training room," Bice said. 
</P>
<P>
Bice also announced the hiring of football coaches at Fullerton and Sonora. Pat 
Ward, an assistant at Chaffey College, was named to replace Steve Nishimoto at 
Fullerton. Nishimoto resigned in December after three seasons to concentrate on 
his teaching assignment. 
</P>
<P>
Terry Cox, varsity football coach at San Gabriel High School, was named varsity 
football coach at Sonora. Cox replaces Larry Allen, who resigned after two 
seasons with a 3-17 record. 
</P>
<P>
Bice said Luczaj, Ward and Bice will begin teaching assignments at their 
schools in two weeks. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
COACHES; HIGH SCHOOL ATHLETICS; FOOTBALL; BUENA PARK HIGH SCHOOL; LUCZAJ, 
MARTIN; FULLERTON HIGH SCHOOL; WARD, PAT; SONORA HIGH SCHOOL; COX, TERRY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA012590-0221 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 167084 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
January 25, 1990, Thursday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
